                    },
                    "body": "So I made a typo in the example... whoooo.\n\nBUT!.... In my actual code it was\/is the correct option (so no typo) thus the problem remains.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=snefit",
